nt Anglophone Nietzsche studies, remains a central text for all concerned with understanding the philosopher's work.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aEternal return. 0aResemblance (Philosophy). 4a19th century. 4aFriedrich Nietzsche. 4aNietzsche. 4ahistory of philosophy. 4ahistory of western philosophy. 4aphilosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Political.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520353633?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520353633423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520353633/original  aEBA_EMB  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles